=== Highlights ===

* ImageJ2 commands and scripts are now macro-recordable ({{GitHub | org=imagej | repo=imagej-legacy | commit=02e9e46296a9fd44962b3cd7ccda12d53183e704 | label=imagej-legacy-02e9}}).
* Script parameters now have reasonable default values ({{GitHub | org=scijava | repo=scijava-ui-swing | commit=7dc0af5e65ee3238f0d5116bba25dd7f35c438e8 | label=scijava-ui-swing-7dc0}}) which can be explicitly set ({{GitHub | org=scijava | repo=scijava-common | commit=3fdc5df4e93577be70d20d994bfc830e5dcb1676 | label=scijava-common-3fdc}}).

== How to update ==

Use the <code>Help > Update</code> command to update your [[ImageJ]] installation. Please send any comments to the [[Mailing Lists|ImageJ mailing list]]. Thank you for the continued feedback and support!

